name: my OBJKTs
description: This tool organizes the OBJKTs associated to a given wallet in 3 main categories: created, owned and swapped or burned. OBJKTs are also grouped by the artist that minted them. If you collected a fake edition from a copyminter, the background will be shown in red. Please burn it! Note that this tool makes queries to the tzkt.io and better-call.dev APIs and it might break in the future. Creator: Javier Gracia Carpio | @jagracar
